@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Document Tools (Scan & OCR & Translate)
actor User
participant "UI (ScanActivity/OcrActivity)" as UI
participant "Camera/Device" as Camera
participant "ScanService (ML Kit)" as MLKit
participant "TranslateService" as TranslateAPI

== Scan and OCR ==
User -> UI : Click "Scan Document"
UI -> Camera : Open Camera
Camera --> UI : Return Image Frame
UI -> MLKit : detect edges and crop
MLKit --> UI : Cropped Image
UI -> MLKit : extractText(image)
activate MLKit
MLKit --> UI : Extracted Text String
deactivate MLKit
UI --> User : Display Extracted Text

== Translate Text ==
User -> UI : Select text, choose target language, click Translate
UI -> TranslateAPI : translate(text, targetLang)
activate TranslateAPI
TranslateAPI --> UI : Translated Text String
deactivate TranslateAPI
UI --> User : Display Translated Text
@enduml
